&lt;li&gt;Internal Comms: Develop clear communication strategies to promote events, share key updates, and manage internal deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operations &amp;amp; Swag: Oversee the Happy Lunch program (invoicing and improvements) and manage the creation and distribution of corporate merchandising for internal events and business fairs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Assistant Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide temporary, ad-hoc support for Executive Assistant (EA) tasks during peak periods or coverage gaps to ensure smooth leadership operations.&lt;/li&gt;
