&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Experimentation lead who will own the evolution of Wallapop&#39;s experimentation practice. This person will define the company&#39;s experimentation standards, improve statistical rigor, increase the speed and quality of product decisions, and help Product teams adopt a culture of evidence-based decision making.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will partner closely with Product, Engineering, Data Science, Analytics, and Executive leadership to ensure experiments are designed, executed, analyzed, and interpreted consistently across the organization. You will be both a hands-on expert and an internal consultant, helping teams answer critical questions about marketplace growth, personalization, search, discovery, trust &amp;amp; safety, monetization, and seller experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
